<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink327">
<l>poṟivarit taṭakkai vēta lañcic</l>
<l>ciṟukaṇ yāṉai nilantoṭal cellā</l>
<l>veyiṉmuḷi cōlaiya vēyuyar curaṉē</l>
<l>yaṉṉa vāriṭai yāṉun</l>
<l>taṇmai ceytavit takaiyōḷ paṇpē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The qualities of this worthy woman brought coolness</l>
<l>even to the path, as harsh as the desert</l>
<l>with tall bamboo and sun-scorched groves,</l>
<l>where elephants with small eyes, being afraid of the heat, </l>
<l>avoid touching the ground with their large trunks </l>
<l>that have dots and lines [on them]. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
